OL,3,CIran reviews 14-point US proposal as
OL,4,CTrump praises 'very good' talks
OL,6,FIran is expected to respond to the
OL,7,Flatest US proposal to end the war on
OL,8,FThursday, it has been reported, as
OL,9,FDonald Trump declared the two nations
OL,10,Fhad "very good" talks.
OL,12,FA one-page 14-point plan has been
OL,13,Fshared with Iran via Pakistani
OL,14,Fmediators, a person familiar with the
OL,15,Fdocument told ITV News' partner CNN.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
