OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778217989
OL,3,CIran reviews 14-point US proposal as
OL,4,CTrump praises 'very good' talks
OL,6,FIf agreed to, the memorandum would
OL,7,Ftrigger a 30-day negotiating period,
OL,8,Fduring which both sides can hash out
OL,9,Fkey issues like nuclear capacity and
OL,10,Ffuture passage through the Strait of
OL,11,FHormuz, the person said.
OL,13,FIt also includes a ban on Iran
OL,14,Fenriching uranium for ten years, a
OL,15,Ftime length that has been brought down
OL,16,Ffrom 20 years during the course of
OL,17,Fnegotiating so-far, the source added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
