OL,3,CIran reviews 14-point US proposal as
OL,4,CTrump praises 'very good' talks
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt comes after Trump said on Wednesday
OL,12,Fthe US had had "very good talks" with
OL,13,FIran over the 24 hours previous, and
OL,14,Finsisted there was "never a deadline"
OL,15,Ffor the nation to respond to the
OL,16,Flatest proposal.
OL,18,F"We're in good shape. Now we're doing
OL,19,Fwell, and we have to get what we have
OL,20,Fto get," Trump said from the Oval
OL,21,FOffice.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
