OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778217989
OL,3,CIran reviews 14-point US proposal as
OL,4,CTrump praises 'very good' talks
OL,6,F"If we don't do that, we'll have to go
OL,7,Fa big step further. But with that
OL,8,Fbeing said, they want to make a deal."
OL,10,FThe US president also claimed that
OL,11,FIran had agreed to not have a nuclear
OL,12,Fweapon, "among other things", but did
OL,13,Fnot give further details.
OL,15,FA two-week ceasefire between the US
OL,16,Fand Iran was agreed on April 7, and
OL,17,Flater extended indefinitely on April
OL,18,F21.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
