OL,3,CIran reviews 14-point US proposal as
OL,4,CTrump praises 'very good' talks
OL,6,FHowever the US has blocked Iranian
OL,7,Fports since April 13, in response to
OL,8,Fthe Strait of Hormuz being almost
OL,9,Fentirely closed by the regime since
OL,10,Fthe war began.
OL,12,FThe US military said on Wednesday it
OL,13,Fhad attacked an Iranian oil tanker in
OL,14,Fthe Gulf of Oman for breaching the
OL,15,Fblockade.
OL,17,FUS Central Command said an American
OL,18,Ffighter jet shot out the rudder of the
OL,19,FIran-flagged tanker after it was
OL,20,Fissued multiple warnings to stop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
