OL,3,CIran reviews 14-point US proposal as
OL,4,CTrump praises 'very good' talks
OL,6,FAt the same time, Israel struck
OL,7,FBeirut's southern suburbs for the
OL,8,Ffirst time since a ceasefire between
OL,9,FIsrael and Lebanon was announced on
OL,10,FApril 17.
OL,12,FFighting between Israel and the
OL,13,FHezbollah militant group has continued
OL,14,Fsince the ceasefire, but mostly in
OL,15,Fsouthern Lebanon.
OL,17,FRescue workers could be seen searching
OL,18,Fthrough the rubble of a destroyed
OL,19,Fbuilding in Beirut on Thursday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
